{"lemma":"بُرْثُنِ","slug":"بُرْثُنِ","root":"ب.ر.ث.ن","root_slug":"ب-ر-ث-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ر-ث-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2181"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AB%D9%8F%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2181","headword_ar":"بُرْثُنٌ","root":"brvn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", of the lion, (AZ, T,) and of any animal of prey, (AZ, As, T, S, M, K,) and of birds, (As, S,) [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"toe;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what corresponds to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSobaE","text_ar":"اـِصْبَع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, As, T, S, M, K;) [in the Lex. of Golius, as on the authority of the S, and in that of Freytag,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"idem quod"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Anmlp","text_ar":"انملة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in homine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this is a mistake, app. occasioned by a mistranscription in a copy of the S;] and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolab","text_ar":"مِخْلَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is its claw, i. e., nail: (AZ, As, T, S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paw"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaf~","text_ar":"كَفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altogether,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbiE","text_ar":"اَصَابِع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"toes"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"claw,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the lion, (Lth, T, M, K,) likened to the instrument for perforating leather; (Lth, T;) and of [all] animals of prey, and of birds that do not prey,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corresponding to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of man:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Th says, of man, it is [termed] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zufor","text_ar":"ظُفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of animals having the kind of foot called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~","text_ar":"خُفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manosimo","text_ar":"مَنْسِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of solidhoofed animals, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfir","text_ar":"حَافِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of cloven-hoofed animals, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zilof","text_ar":"ظِلْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of beasts and birds of prey, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolab","text_ar":"مِخْلَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and of birds that do not prey, and of dogs and the like, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovun","text_ar":"بُرْثُن"},{"kind":"text","text":"; though it may be also used [in like manner] of all animals of prey: (Msb:) [but properly] it is of birds that do not prey, as the crow-kind, and the pigeon; (M;) and sometimes, of the [lizard called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~","text_ar":"ضَبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) and of the rat, or mouse, and of the jerboa: (M:) and is, in the pl. form, (M, TA,) which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAvinu","text_ar":"بَرَاثِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, TA,) metaphorically applied, by Sá'ideh Ibn-Jueiyeh, to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fingers"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man gathering honey [deposited by wild bees in a hollow of a rock]. (M, * TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovunu AlA^asadi","text_ar":"بُرْثُنُ الاَسَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain brand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mark made with a hot iron, upon camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the form of the claw of the lion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  This, also, is the name of a sword of Marthad Ibn-'Alas. (K.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovunapN","text_ar":"بُرْثُنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to signify the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovunN","text_ar":"بُرْثُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraAvinu","text_ar":"بَرَاثِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": for] Temeem are termed in a trad. the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovumap","text_ar":"بُرْثُمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burojumap","text_ar":"بُرْجُمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the tribes of Mudar; and El-Khattábee says that it should be the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"burovunap","text_ar":"بُرْثُنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (assumed tropical:)  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"claw,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"claws;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning thereby their impetuous valour, and strength: but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brvmp","text_ar":"برثمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brvnp","text_ar":"برثنة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be substituted for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the purpose of assimilation [to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brjmp","text_ar":"برجمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","T","As","S","M","K","Lth","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}